short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Integration powered by JetWave CRM Plus

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
An API integration platform providing database driven screen pops. Integrate your phone system with your favorite CRMs like Salesforce, Freshsales, Zendesk etc. Give your customer service agents a jumpstart into knowing exactly who's calling them without making your customers wait to look up account identifying information. 

This extension will also recognize and convert phone numbers presented in Chrome and transform them into clickable links for a seamless click to dial experience. 

This extension will only work with your Jet Wave service cloud hosted PBX."
